        requires forall|i: int| 0 <= i < sub.len() ==>
            exists|j: int| 0 <= j < sup.len() && (#[trigger] sup[j]).0 == (#[trigger] sub[i]).0,
        ensures spec_entries_to_map(sub).dom().subset_of(spec_entries_to_map(sup).dom()),

        decreases entries.len(),
